                    h3 Malware
                    p By following the instructions of tech support scammers, victims could unknowingly download and install harmful software onto their computers or other personal devices.
                    p By installing malware on your device, scammers can gain complete control over your computer, enabling them to steal your data, gain complete access over your online accounts, hold your data for ransom, and potentially monitor your activity.
 
